\": \"their fans\", \"from\": 1283, \"to\": 1293}, {\"ngram\": \"endorsement commitments\", \"from\": 1317, \"to\": 1340}, {\"ngram\": \"a safe environment\", \"from\": 1388, \"to\": 1406}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are proud of many of our athletes who use their platform to raise awareness on important issues, including speaking out about online abuse and its impact on mental health,\\\" he added.\", \"from\": 1410, \"to\": 1596, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our athletes\", \"from\": 1435, \"to\": 1447}, {\"ngram\": \"their platform\", \"from\": 1456, \"to\": 1470}, {\"ngram\": \"awareness\", \"from\": 1480, \"to\": 1489}, {\"ngram\": \"important issues\", \"from\": 1493, \"to\": 1509}, {\"ngram\": \"online abuse\", \"from\": 1540, \"to\": 1552}, {\"ngram\": \"its impact\", \"from\": 1557, \"to\": 1567}, {\"ngram\": \"mental health\", \"from\": 1571, \"to\": 1584}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He said World Athletics would use the research to \\\"drive positive change\\\".\", \"from\": 1598, \"to\": 1672, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1606, \"end\": 1621, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics\", \"score\": 0.9999999999661213, \"rank\": 3.387949416288226e-11, \"text\": \"World Athletics\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the research\", \"from\": 1632, \"to\": 1644}, {\"ngram\": \"positive change\", \"from\": 1655, \"to\": 1670}]}, {\"sentence\": \"HOUSE RULES\", \"from\": 1674, \"to\": 1685, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"HOUSE RULES\", \"from\": 1674, \"to\": 1685}]}]}"